{"tid":1266973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［七一野餐團］630 晚/ 71 早 將 於 煲 底 同 修 頓 集 合","createTime":"2019-06-29T16:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T14:55:32.000Z","uid":213379,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ee30d6276dd49ca296209d40be376c2e5fb53ef9","tid":1266973,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:46:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">七一野餐會 <br />\n人數決定一切</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔理三七廿一<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n朝早頭班車 你地同我出黎 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n</span></span>塞滿金鐘灣仔站 <br />\n<br />\n一齊由月台上去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n記住準備好餐具同帶齊餐具野餐<br />\n<br />\n記住準備好餐具同帶齊餐具野餐<br />\n<br />\n記住準備好餐具同帶齊餐具野餐<br />\n<br />\n記住準備好餐具同帶齊餐具野餐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可帶少量食物 聽講某狗種最近鍾意食雞蛋 除雞蛋外 帶咩都無所謂 放題式野餐</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">記住所有行動人數決定一齊 唔出黎仲等到幾時？</span></span><br />\n<br />\nMy friend, be water 量力而為"},{"pid":"a796077c8ff1bf4246c89ad288db6d69110cdfee","tid":1266973,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a310baa0156da7f72a5da8c44d5d7462e4f926","tid":1266973,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:46:46.000Z","msg":"記住準備好餐具同帶齊餐具野餐"},{"pid":"6a4c18f651518c3de73769276d2aecbd4a522c53","tid":1266973,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:46:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4b564f1131b0f4109e766270791a687d9caa96","tid":1266973,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:47:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"090c0867f5e631be4ab1a970540f0